title: Sarah Jarosz 🔥 mandolin solo on "Jealous Moon" #music #mandolin
description:
Watch Sarah Jarosz play the mandolin break in her song "Jealous Moon" during a live performance recorded in The Current studio. 

Sarah Jarosz’s 2024 album, "Polaroid Lovers," is available on @rounderrecords.

Sarah Jarosz – mandolin, vocals
Eric Doob – drums
Michael Rinne – bass
Seth Taylor – guitar, vocals
